  "title": "Raw Raspberry Brownie Truffle",
  "subtitle": "A thermometer pays for itself the first time.",
  "excerpt": "Raw Raspberry Brownie Truffle. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
